import React, { useState } from 'react' import Header from './Header' import '../styles/NewExercise.css' const NewExercise = () => { const [exercise, setExercise] = useState({ name: '', equipment: '', fullName: '', description: '', video: '' }) const handleChange = (key, value) => { exercise[key] = value console.log(exercise) } const onSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault() } return (
handleChange('name', e.target.value)} /> handleChange('video', e.target.value)} /> handleChange('description', e.target.value)} />
) } export default NewExercise
